snippet.title: Character Demo - "Lynette: Cat in the Box" | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
In a gift box that appeared out of nowhere, something seems to be moving, making you want to lift the lid to find out what's inside.
—Keep your eyes open, don't get fooled!
The cat might not be inside, but instead lurking in the corner and awaiting its prey.
